  <brief_title>Brain Imaging Study of Brain Plasticity in Chronic Stroke Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Functional Magnetic Resonance Imaging and Diffusion Tensor Imaging Study About Reorganization and Recovery Mechanism of Brain Neural Network for Chronic Stroke Patients</official_title>
